claim.claim-text:
19. The method of controlling the temperature of a brewed beverage in the brewed beverage dispenser as in claim 13 further comprising the steps of:
calculating a heating time during which the brewed beverage in the dispenser is heated;
activating the heater to heat the brewed beverage for a period proximate to a start of the heating time;
deactivating the heating during the heating time; and
activating the heater for at least one more time period before expiration of the heating time.
